    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "學生將依照以下情境進行英語聽講訓練:<br>1.全球問候禮儀<br>2.亞洲節慶<br>3.柬埔寨的塗鴉文化<br>4.家事<br>5.亞洲藝術節慶<br>6.世界旅遊<br>7.國際食物與餐桌禮儀<br>8.健康與健身<br>9.時尚與服裝<br>10.電腦科技與發明<br>11.電影<br>12.友誼<br>",
        "en": "Students will develop listening and speaking ability in English in the following contexts:<br>1.Greetings around the world<br>2.Interesting festivals in Asia<br>3.Ancient graffiti discovered in Cambodia<br>4.Housework<br>5.The Asia Art Festival<br>6.Travel<br>7.International food and table manners<br>8.Health and Fitness<br>9.Fashion and Clothing<br>10.Computer Technology<br>11.Movies<br>12.Friendship<br>"
    },
